cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with text processing and sentiment classification. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it proposes a new architecture for deep learning. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it deals with convolutional neural networks, and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it proposes a new method for evaluating the convolution operation.
